Toast @sourdough bread{2%slices}. Wash and dry produce.

Thinly slice @fresh mozzarella{4%ounces} into rounds. Thinly slice @tomato{1} into rounds; season with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

In a #large bowl{}, combine @arugula{2%ounces}, @Parmesan cheese{3%tablespoons}, and a drizzle of @olive oil{1%teaspoon}. Season lightly with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

Spread @guacamole{1/2%cup} onto toasted bread. Season with salt, pepper, and a pinch of @chili flakes{1%teaspoon}. Top with mozzarella and seasoned tomato.

Halve toasts on a diagonal; divide toasts and salad between #plates{}. Drizzle everything with as much @balsamic glaze{5%teaspoons} as you like. Serve.